reviewText:
First DVD video for Boeing 787 flight with special livery for ANA Airways, film taken in Okayama Airport. Besides, other special livery includes Pocket Monster, Golden Colour ANA Airways, Lavender for China Airlines to celebrate the new route for Tai Pei - Sapporo, Japan.

Other than B787, Boeing Deam Lifter are also included in this video with amazing views in approx. 4hrs. Don't miss it.
